    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that but my doctor is super busy and honestly i kinda feel like he just dismisses me when i talk about side effects. i just want something that works without the chemicals. i read on a few forums that if u just take the SJW instead, it's much smoother. is there like a specific way to do it so i don't get those withdrawal things you mentioned? like can i just take both for a couple days to transition?",
