      "content": "Serotonin syndrome is a serious reaction, and mixing serotonergic agents like sertraline and St. John's wort significantly increases this risk. Even small doses combined can put you in danger, and this is not something you should try to manage on your own. Please reach out to a nurse hotline or visit an urgent care clinic immediately; they can help you with medication management safely while you wait to see your primary doctor.",
